       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. BASIC-TEST.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-AMOUNT PIC 9(5)V99 VALUE 100.50.
       01 WS-RATE   PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE 5.25.
       01 WS-RESULT PIC 9(7)V99.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-MAIN.
           COMPUTE WS-RESULT = WS-AMOUNT * WS-RATE / 100.
           DISPLAY WS-RESULT.
           STOP RUN.
